**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************
	BLOCKS
**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************

Note: block.recall
- resets recall variable before each run and resets the studyWords_currentList items
- randomly selects the next recall list from list.recallLists and fills the
studyWords_currentList items with the items of the selected List (using 24 conditionals)
<block recall>
/ onblockbegin = [
	values.listCount += 1;
	values.recallListCount += 1;
	values.RecallWordEstimate = 0;
	values.positionLure_Recall = 0;
	values.Recall = "";
	values.nr_otherRecalledWords = 0;
	values.countCorrect_Recall = 0;
	values.intrusionOther = "";
	
	item.studyWords_currentList.reset();
	item.lure_currentList.reset();
	
	values.nextList = list.recallLists.nextValue;	
	if (values.nextList == 1){
